      <title>美国国债价格上涨，有望创三年来最长涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/treasuries-climb-set-for-longest-winning-streak-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债价格上涨拉开了全球债券市场多事之周的序幕，美国国债价格有望连续第三个月上涨，这将是三年来持续时间最长的上涨行情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/treasuries-climb-set-for-longest-winning-streak-in-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 13:02:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型零售商扩大产品范围以抵消消费疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-29/retailers-expand-their-offerings-to-offset-weak-spending-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CFRA 高级副总裁 Arun Sundaram 表示，过去两年消费者支出一直在下降。但他表示，大型零售商现在正在扩大产品范围以增加市场份额，他们的股票也在上涨。他正在接受“彭博监测”的采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-29/retailers-expand-their-offerings-to-offset-weak-spending-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 13:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>垃圾借款人涌入市场，推出数十亿美元的新债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/junk-borrowers-rush-into-market-with-billions-in-new-offerings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于借款人希望利用信贷市场的强劲势头，皇家加勒比邮轮公司和海洋世界等一批垃圾级债券发行人于周一开始发行债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/junk-borrowers-rush-into-market-with-billions-in-new-offerings</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 13:00:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国太阳能发电量创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/germany-s-solar-power-generation-surges-to-a-fresh-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着可再生能源在价格昂贵的化石燃料发电中所占的份额越来越大，德国不断扩大的太阳能电池板阵列创下了新一代发电记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/germany-s-solar-power-generation-surges-to-a-fresh-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:59:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
